                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base"
                        >
                            Automated data entries and marketing <br
                                class="hidden lg:block"
                            />leads accelerate response time by over <br
                                class="hidden lg:block"
                            />
                            <span class="text-[#007BFF] font-bold">12%.</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="real_time_benifits_card md:text-center lg:text-right p-2 md:p-3 lg:py-4 lg:pr-4 mt-5 md:mt-7 lg:mt-12"
                    >
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base"
                        >
                            <span class="text-[#007BFF] font-bold"
                                >230+
                            </span>Manpower hours saved(every <br
                                class="hidden lg:block"
                            /> month) through the automated <br
                                class="hidden lg:block"
                            />assignment of leads and inquiries.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div class="flex justify-center">
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={crm_page_realtime_benifits}
                            alt="crm_page_realtime_benifits"
                            class=""
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="real_time_benifits_card text-center p-2 md:p-3 lg:p-4 mt-3 lg:mt-5"
                    >
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base"
                        >
                            <span class="text-[#007BFF] font-bold">97%</span> customer
                            retention due to a <br class="hidden lg:block" /> personalized
                            and customer-centric <br class="hidden lg:block" />
                            approach.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid-3">
                    <div
                        class="real_time_benifits_card text-center lg:text-left p-2 md:p-3 lg:py-4 lg:pl-4 md:mt-2 lg:mt-14"
